* That I'd kill you *

38:25.847 --> 38:28.516
* 'Cause I loved you *

38:29.142 --> 38:31.811
* Yeah *

38:37.567 --> 38:39.235
Do you have it?

38:40.236 --> 38:41.571
Yes.

38:42.447 --> 38:46.910
We're going to take you
and Caspian to a facility

38:46.951 --> 38:49.829
where there are people
who can help you.

38:51.206 --> 38:54.542
Do you understand
what I'm telling you?

38:55.502 --> 38:57.337
I grow old again?

38:57.379 --> 38:58.713
Yes.

39:00.006 --> 39:01.758
You can't take it away.

39:01.800 --> 39:04.010
We just don't have
a choice, Subash.

39:04.052 --> 39:07.138
You can't take away
what it gave me.

39:08.807 --> 39:11.851
The miracle of life.

39:11.893 --> 39:14.020
I just needed
to feel it again.

39:14.062 --> 39:17.440
And after this,
I'm going to fight

39:17.482 --> 39:20.276
for every last day.

39:27.242 --> 39:29.536
I happen to know
you have stronger Debris

39:29.577 --> 39:31.996
that can access
communication frequencies.

39:32.038 --> 39:33.581
Why would you want this one?

39:33.623 --> 39:35.333
Because it works.

39:36.960 --> 39:39.879
Is that the only reason?

39:39.921 --> 39:43.800
Because this trade,
this method,

39:43.842 --> 39:46.136
Tarkolov,
it's unusual for you.

39:47.137 --> 39:49.097
I'm good.

39:50.056 --> 39:52.851
I hope you know
what you're doing.

39:53.852 --> 39:56.271
You always worry too much.

40:03.903 --> 40:06.239
(door closes)

40:12.579 --> 40:14.789
You can.

40:18.626 --> 40:20.503
Trust me.

40:21.463 --> 40:24.758
I know it wasn't easy going
against your orders.

40:24.799 --> 40:27.218
I appreciate that you did that.

40:28.428 --> 40:32.807
Ferris told me to tell you
that my father was in Greece,

40:32.849 --> 40:35.977
and I have no idea why.

40:36.019 --> 40:40.148
It's like she's leaving
just enough bread crumbs

40:40.190 --> 40:42.901
for Maddox to
figure something out.

40:43.818 --> 40:46.905
-Do you know what that is?
-No.

40:46.946 --> 40:49.449
But it was important
enough for her to do it.

40:49.491 --> 40:52.952
She's using me to figure
something out about my father.

40:52.994 --> 40:55.413
I have a bad feeling about it.

40:56.498 --> 40:59.167
I can't trust Ferris.

41:01.086 --> 41:03.088
And you can't trust Maddox.

41:04.381 --> 41:07.967
FINOLA: MI6 suspects
that he's been working
against the coalition,

41:08.009 --> 41:09.928
most likely the Chinese.

41:12.347 --> 41:14.474
You're wrong.

41:14.516 --> 41:16.726
I'm giving you
the information that I have...

41:16.768 --> 41:18.061
You don't know what
you're saying.

41:18.103 --> 41:22.649
This man... saved my life.

41:23.316 --> 41:25.735
The only thing
that I know for sure

41:25.777 --> 41:29.656
is that something
is going on that both of us
don't even understand.

41:29.698 --> 41:31.408
We need to trust each other.

41:31.449 --> 41:34.911
That is the only way we're
going to find our answers.

41:34.953 --> 41:37.914
Is there anything
that I need to know?

41:40.041 --> 41:41.710
Is there anything--

41:41.751 --> 41:44.212
They're surveilling
your apartment.

41:51.803 --> 41:53.722
(elevator dings)

41:53.763 --> 41:56.057
(phone rings)

41:58.101 --> 41:59.728
-(elevator dings)
-What's up?

41:59.769 --> 42:01.146
We've traced the calls

42:01.187 --> 42:02.856
that came in
on Anson Ash's phone.

42:02.897 --> 42:05.817
It's from a cell phone
in Maine.

42:05.859 --> 42:07.777
Stay on it.

42:07.819 --> 42:09.779
I want a name.

42:10.613 --> 42:12.157
(elevator dings)

42:27.797 --> 42:29.674
MAN: Orbital investigating.

42:29.716 --> 42:31.051
(beep)

42:32.135 --> 42:34.804
Debris field 16, 27.

42:34.846 --> 42:36.431
(beep)

42:36.473 --> 42:37.724
21.

42:37.766 --> 42:39.225
(beep)

42:39.976 --> 42:41.311
56.

42:41.353 --> 42:42.437
(beep)

42:43.521 --> 42:44.814
170.

42:44.856 --> 42:46.107
(beep)
